%r
#Question2

a.features=iris
a.features$Species<-NULL
View(a.features) #species have been removed


b<-kmeans(a.features,3,nstart=20) 

table(a$Species,b$cluster) #to view between the species and the cluster

library(ggplot2)
ggplot(data=a, aes(x=Petal.Length, y=Petal.Width,color=b$cluster)) + 
  geom_point() #plot the graph using ggplot2 and cluster the iris

%r
#Question3
a<-iris
summary(a) #to read the data of iris

a.features=iris
a.features$Species<-NULL
View(a.features) #species have been removed


b<-kmeans(a.features,3,nstart=20) 

table(a$Species,b$cluster) #to view between the species and the cluster

library(ggplot2)
ggplot(data=a, aes(x=Petal.Length, y=Petal.Width, shape=a$Species, color=b$cluster)) + 
  geom_point()+stat_ellipse() #plot the graph using ggplot2 and cluster the iris
